<br>
I have read a few things here and there I I want to be sure I have it straight.<br>
<br>
1. The group leaders Alignment controls who can join the group.<br>
<br>
2. what are the limits though can OG group with ON,N,NG only, but not with DG,DN,DE,NE,LE? There fore allowing N To Group with All.<br>
<br>
3. This then also effects the ability to &quot;buff&quot; in a similar way Correct?<br>
<br>
Aramond<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uroawen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Roawen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 35<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/18/02 1:54:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1145.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Qusetion on Grouping and Alignment</span><hr size=1> Order Good, Neutral Good, Discord Good can all group<br>
Order Neutral, Neutral Neutral, Discord Neutral can all group<br>
Order Evil, Neutral Evil, Discord Evil can all group<br>
<br>
Any Good can group with Good or Neutral<br>
Any Evil can group with Evil or Neutral<br>
Any Neutral can group with Evil or Good<br>
~~<br>
Order grouped with Order, Discord grouped with Discord, Neutral grouped with Neutral gets an exp BONUS<br>
<br>
Order grouped with Discord gets an exp PENALTY<br>
<br>
Order OR Discord grouped with Neutral gets NORMAL exp<br>
~~<br>
Good can buff any Good or Neutral<br>
Evil can buff any Evil or Neutral<br>
Neutral can buff any Good or Evil <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukimayasilverbark.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kimaya Silverbark</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.alienexplorer.com/clipart/images5/wolf.pawprint2.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 80<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/18/02 2:00:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1145.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.bellsouth.net/coDataImages/bellsouthpwp/Groups/15/15568/pages/34736/Kimaya-60.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Qusetion on Grouping and Alignment</span><hr size=1> It was my understanding that neutrals never get an exp bonus, whether they're grouped with order, discord or neutral.  (The idea being that they already have a bonus by not being restricted.)<br>
