The trick around this is to have several invites open at the same time, without accepting. That is the neutral leader issues an invite to the good and evil members, with neither of them pressing accept. Only after they are both invited,  do they accept and now a mixed group has formed. They still cannot heal/buff between them. And I'm not sure about any Exp. penalty this might entail.<br>
